body:
Bumps [toxic](https://github.com/TokTok/toxic) from `f012007` to `b77bff3`.
Commits
  • b77bff3 Add config man entries for colour scheme options
  • eb964b6 Fix off by one error and comment magic numbers
  • 2ff9d29 Custom colors proof of concept
  • 2640919 Don't announce when ghost peers leave the group
  • 2fcbc4f Remove lots of duplicate code related to printing timestamps
  • 4330bf5 Show peer join/part messages in conferences
  • 3f1b7cd Update config example and some default settings to reflect recent changes
  • 1e985c1 Interface improvements and bump to v0.10.0
  • 61740bd Fix a couple minor issues
  • 0d8e6d7 Update readme screenshot and bump to v0.9.1
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
